title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 11 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 11 2021
description:
Kyle Rittenhouse's mom takes on Biden for smearing her child, says he's not racist, not a white supremacist and they don't know him. Twitter throttles Buck's correct (and witty) tweet on masks. But the left can't stop us because we're right and they're wrong -- although they never change their narrative points, even when they know they are wrong. NYC Mayor-Elect Eric Adams stands up to BLM. C&B take calls on Open Line Friday.
